metadata.name: Jar of greed
metadata.description:
Any new opportunity, any new beginning, needs to be treated with a different level of consciousness than the one from which it came. 
To get there, you need to calm down, to strip yourself from what you think it is "yourself", you need to desintegrate everything in order to re-build the new version: the one of the mind and body carring your dreams.
To get there, you need to expose yourself, accept the mistakes, the error404, the capital sins in all of us and also what concepts and accions we did  that made us what we are today. 

1/1

Shot details:
2017
from the collection "Art Hysteria"
